, CIUFES 0795-1, 61.8 mm SL, female, Ilhas Escalvada, Guarapari, 
<normalizedToken id="C5A5E126C301FBECDC73A94D09BC8563" originalValue="Espírito">Espirito</normalizedToken>
Santo, Brazil. Photograph by Raphael M. Macieira.
</paragraph>
</caption>
