<taxonomicName id="5575A41875A9D087BD3EF9B7BC5CAA2F" class="Actinopterygii" family="Opistognathidae" genus="Opistognathus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Opistognathus aurifrons" order="Perciformes" pageId="23" pageNumber="118" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aurifrons">Opistognathus aff. aurifrons</taxonomicName>
, juvenile, Fernando de Noronha Archipelago, Brazil. Photograph by 
<normalizedToken id="1BE565382BF5EBB266C18A76A8D47A5B" originalValue="João">Joao</normalizedToken>
P. Krajewski.
</paragraph>
